Billy Joe Saunders and Chris Eubank Jnr are due to fight at Wembley Arena on May 9 . 
  The pair met in November and Saunders won the fight over 12 rounds . 
  Saunders is due to challenge for the WBO middleweight title in July . 
  Both men were involved in a war of words at a press conference on Thursday . 
  Eubanks challenged Saunders to take a re-match with him in May . 
  Frank Warren has suggested an autumn rematch for the pair . 
 